    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Proofs designated by the artist to serve as the standard, both aesthetically and technically, for the printing of the edition. Sometimes identical with the printers' proofs of the edition.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
